- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper discusses the architecture of Optiplan and its performance in a planning competition, which could involve algorithmic and data structure considerations. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper discusses the engineering aspects of developing Optiplan as a planning system.
